title: 055 - My Name Is Lyman Zerga
description: On today's show, the guys discuss Will Ferrell and Rachel McAdams new Netflix movie, Eurovision, and how Zito seems to be the only person who liked it. They also chat about the Netflix show "Home Game," which gets a passing grade, and go through the Folder of Death which includes topics such as which actress is the most attractive in which movie, gators eating each other, a listener question from Scotland, and the guys start to compile their lists for their Top 5 Big Fat Stooges. Enjoy.
